data.name: GetAccessoriesType
data.value: Select AccessoriesTypeId, AccessoriesType from [UnicoVehicle].[master].[AccessoriesType] where DeletedDate is null

data.name: GetAccessoriesTypebyId
data.value: Select AccessoriesType from [UnicoVehicle].[master].[AccessoriesType] where DeletedDate is null and AccessoriesTypeId = @accessoriesTypeId

data.name: UpdateAccessoriesType
data.value: Update [UnicoVehicle].[master].[AccessoriesType] set ModifiedDate = @modifiedDate, AccessoriesType = @accessoriesType where AccessoriesTypeId = @accessoriesTypeId
